<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
</app>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Hansen Mawrer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> czu reden von geleits wegen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern und
                                <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und kauffmanschaft. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        sache etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Jacobi anno
                                <expan>deci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>. </ab></div>
</div></body>
